name: Mustard Cafe Goa

reviews.review_text:
I visited the Mustard Cafe Goa today on (5 th December 2024) with my mother.
The food was delectable, The service was excellent. I truly enjoyed the meal. My mom also ordered Pineapple juice and she loved it very much. It was our first cafe visit in GOA and the entire experience was delightful. Thank you so much for great hospitality Team Mustard Cafe.

I would never imagine having a delicious Bengali meal in Goa but Arjun and I did! And what a sweet find it was. The seating is slightly uncomfortable because the restaurant is placed on a slope but the food makes up for the discomfort. We got the non-veg thali and an extra dish- the calamari and chorizo. My fav on the thali was the chicken curry! Do go here because the food is great and the service is good .

We recently had the pleasure of having lunch in Mustard cafe, Goa.The cafe is very leafy and nicely decorated. Definitely worth going here!

The Nonveg bengali thali platter was just awesome, whereas French cuisine was delicious. They have different types of great cocktails and healthy coolers.

Overall, our experience at Mustard Cafe was decent, leaving us with a satisfying taste of both French and Bengali flavors.

Food: 5/5
Service: 4/5
Ambience: 4/5

### Mustard Cafe Goa: A Culinary Haven in Tivim

Tucked away in the vibrant region of Tivim, Mustard Cafe Goa boasts an impressive rating of 4.6 stars, as celebrated by over 1,320 satisfied diners. This charming eatery has become a sought-after destination for those craving a fusion of flavors, especially its standout offerings of **French cuisine** and **Bengali delicacies**. Customers have particularly raved about their delightful **cocktails**, making this cafe a must-visit spot for cocktail enthusiasts and food lovers alike.

### Ambiance & Design

Upon stepping into Mustard Cafe, patrons are greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The café is adorned with lush greenery, creating a leafy retreat perfect for both intimate meals and friendly gatherings. The décor is tastefully curated, showcasing a blend of contemporary aesthetics and cozy charm. Though some reviewers noted that the seating arrangement can feel slightly uncomfortable due to the building’s slope, the overwhelming ambiance makes up for it. The gentle strumming of live music enhances the dining experience, enveloping guests in a relaxed and enjoyable space.

![Cafe Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdks0txym4eCJSXJXiyMonQEKxgIQDrf7ij7ia-YodiB2diyepk7Q-8YT_QdYxGAxiu8Rk-hgAAUuUz5om1q9BrAx5gexJgQCU96G1B0CRKggRJ0D6pi9THKd-xsEeQ_JnSlBwW6Sw=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Mustard Cafe's menu is a delightful tapestry of culinary influences, with a strong emphasis on both **French and Bengali cuisines**. Signature dishes like the **Non-veg Bengali thali** and **French classics** have received high praise from diners. Reviewers have highlighted the **chicken curry** from the thali as a standout, while the restaurant’s cocktails have also caught the eye, offering a refreshing complement to the rich flavors of the food.

The presentation of dishes is equally impressive, as reflected in the stunning plates captured in customer photos, which showcase a colorful and appetizing array. With options for both omnivores and vegetarians, including healthy coolers, there’s something for everyone at this culinary gem.

![Cocktails](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnO33qKi18cvDe9OR9y6VWblQ4y5SNtwxZyxBWN9y8smPz-Q5gcWFsFd6KHolJajUXeQXGzyxfpWGDQaNgxXB8wr389PB7n26OKtlcoiXysDubZRhMaOehn6ILQekaWcWlPgwDU=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

Guests frequently commend the attentive service at Mustard Cafe. The hospitality provided by the staff has left many diners feeling valued, with one customer expressing their gratitude for the exceptional service during their visit with family. The café seems to have struck a harmonious balance between efficiency and warmth, making each patron's experience memorable.

### Popularity & Reviews

The positive buzz surrounding Mustard Cafe is infectious on social media platforms, where food lovers share photos of their colorful dishes and cocktails. Critics and patrons alike echo the sentiment that Mustard Cafe is a worthwhile culinary exploration, whether you are immersed in the rich flavors of Bengal or indulging in French cuisine. The seamless blend of flavors and atmosphere has contributed to its high ratings and steadfast popularity as a dining destination.

![Delicious Spread](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdnm-V0gkNE8gME8QStehIdAgI6-M6kHcWbCpoxr4xXNray9clSNzzN02XF8eiFQwzC1yJD56TsAyQwkGWjAbeTthSBlBU-U1nH4usoxeq0vplWf_1o5gyWPxnMMni14ZYkv3WRj=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In summary, Mustard Cafe Goa stands out as a vibrant dining hotspot in Tivim, where culinary craftsmanship meets a charming atmosphere. With a focus on **cocktails**, **French cuisine**, and **Bengali specialties**, this cafe is not just a meal; it’s a flavorful journey worth taking. Whether you’re a local resident or visiting Goa, Mustard Cafe promises an exceptional dining experience that tantalizes the taste buds and warms the heart.
